; Coverage test for commodity.cc
; Tests commodity_t::print with quoted commodity symbols.
; The "elide_quotes" path in print() removes quotes when the symbol
; contains non-digit characters and COMMODITY_STYLE_SEPARATED is set.

2024/01/15 Test
    Assets:Stocks          10 "AA BB" @ $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
               $-500
            10 AA BB  Assets
               $-500    Cash
            10 AA BB    Stocks
--------------------
               $-500
            10 AA BB
end test
